<emphasis id="1DDEC4610D32A400FF68F9713E3F00DE" bold="true" box="[189,324,1712,1738]" pageId="3" pageNumber="161">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2F1518730D32A400FF68F91F3BAC00ED" blockId="3.[189,1239,1758,1785]" box="[189,1239,1758,1785]" pageId="3" pageNumber="161">
<emphasis id="1DDEC4610D32A400FF68F91F3E4900EC" box="[189,306,1758,1784]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="161">Apelqvisti</emphasis>
, named after one of the collectors, Niklas Apelqvist (formerly Niklas Jönsson).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
